Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.26,0:00:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been a physician and a psychiatrist for 35 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.26,0:00:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've worked in the field of psychoanalysis and psychotherapy and group therapy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,psychodynamics of the various schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done a lot of research on nutrition and its relationship to brain chemistry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.88,0:00:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and its relationship to mental illness and emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.80,0:00:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,For the last 10 years, I've been doing research into the nature of consciousness itself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and the applications of that knowledge that came out of that research
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to an understanding of that field of knowledge which the world calls spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, inherent in what we're talking about today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is that relationship between body, mind, and spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.59,0:00:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And what does that really mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.05,0:00:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that something scientific that we can clinically verify?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.93,0:00:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is that some kind of a New Age fantasy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Our talk for today will be about the prevention of stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.14,0:01:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.34,0:01:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.88,0:01:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A subject about which we read so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.60,0:01:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Its implications for health.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.30,0:01:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Its implications for emotional and psychological health.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Its meaning in industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Its meaning in business.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.00,0:01:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The realization now of wide areas in our culture
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.30,0:01:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of being aware of what stress means,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.96,0:01:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,what's implied in this disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.91,0:01:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And so today we will need to look closely at what this relationship is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.59,0:01:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,between the body and its response to stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.63,0:01:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind and how this relates to spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:01:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll be covering today how stress results from a point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.52,0:01:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It results from what we are holding in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,From our attitudes and our beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll see that the source of stress is within ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.12,0:01:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really not in the world at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.64,0:01:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no such thing as escaping stress
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.62,0:02:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,because its source, its cause, is within us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Its source.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.50,0:02:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Its source is not within the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we'll be reversing the way the mind usually looks at things
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,about cause and effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see that cause is not in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and effect in mind, but vice versa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That the level of power, the level of cause,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is held in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And this brings about our experiences of what happens in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.20,0:02:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Our folklore intuitively knows this
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.62,0:02:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,because it says,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.18,0:02:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,one man's meat is another man's poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.48,0:02:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,One man's meat is another man's poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And in that we have the secret of what we're looking at today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The power is not in the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The power is not something out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.86,0:02:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of creating our experience
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of all events in life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,lie within us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.64,0:02:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's by reowning our power then
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that we can learn how to prevent stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.52,0:03:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So we will be talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,methods of precluding stress
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of treating its aftermath.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The so-called stress reduction programs
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,which are so commonly available in our society today
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.18,0:03:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,are really methods of handling
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the effects of stress once it's already happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The relaxation programs
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to relieve the tension within the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You might say,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the horse is already out of the barn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.18,0:03:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be looking at ways
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.14,0:03:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,to offset this
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.14,0:03:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,so that the tension never arises in the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.14,0:03:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,These various ways of handling stress
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.14,0:03:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,in the medical model.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I recently got a brochure, in fact this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It says stress and heart disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.17,0:03:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stress and heart disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And right there we have a whole program.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a whole program which the mind has bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That stress is something out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stress is something inherent in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That the result of stress,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to affect the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.17,0:04:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The heart with all its symbolic meaning to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The various papers then had to do
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,really with heart disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The consequence of stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming about through our levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and manifesting within the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Because all things are experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,within consciousness then today,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll be looking at that relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,between body, mind and spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And in this talk, as we have in other talks,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,we want to go back
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and carefully define
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,things that you can verify
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,through your own experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And in this talk as well as the other talks
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to be talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,clinical verifiable experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.86,0:04:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming from the viewpoint of the skeptical scientist
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.86,0:04:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,who believes only what can be clinically repeated
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and which he can verify through his own inner experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we invite you during this talk
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to find out within yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth of all that we are talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,To begin with we notice that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the body itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.44,0:05:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,a characteristic of the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is that it is insentient.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That is, the body has no capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to experience itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean that the arm in and of itself
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot experience its own existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It cannot experience its own armness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.44,0:05:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It cannot experience that it is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,much less where it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,or how big it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.44,0:05:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,or what it's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we know what's going on with the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We know because of the senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.56,0:05:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So we don't experience the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,we experience the senses reporting this of the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.04,0:05:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The senses themselves have no capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to experience themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,An ear, the vibrations going through the eighth nerve,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,vibrating the tympanic membrane, etc.,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,has no way to experience itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.20,0:06:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does experience of the body
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,take place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes place in something greater than that,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and that we call mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So all experience of the body is occurring
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,in an energy field, in a level,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that we call mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind itself, very curiously,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,has no capacity to experience itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,An amazing thought until you look into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.13,0:06:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see that a thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.13,0:06:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,of and by itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.13,0:06:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,has no capacity to experience its own thoughtness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A memory has no capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,in and of itself
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.45,0:06:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to experience its own memoryness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A fantasy about the future
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,has no capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Our imagination, our emotions,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,all that goes on in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,is only experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.45,0:06:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,because of a greater and larger
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,energy field than mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is what we call consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:07:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,An energy field more diffuse
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.45,0:07:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and formless,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,capable of experiencing change,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.45,0:07:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,capable of experiencing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.45,0:07:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,any phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It is because of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that we're aware
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.12,0:07:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of what is going on in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It is because of mind
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,we're aware of what is going on with sensations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of sensations
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,we're aware of what goes on
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,with the physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Curiously enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,even consciousness itself
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot report what is going on
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,within itself
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,except for a field which is infinite
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and without dimension
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and called the absolute knowingness
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.63,0:07:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,or awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.63,0:07:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It is because of awareness,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,it is because of that quality
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.63,0:07:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,of awareness which goes with our existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes with our beingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because we are,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,we're capable of awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of awareness then comes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the knowingness of what goes on
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.63,0:07:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,within consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness reporting to us
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.63,0:08:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,what is going on within mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind reporting what goes on
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,with sensations about the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we can see
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that that which we are,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,when we say I or me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,in its highest and greatest sense,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,we're talking about the capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.63,0:08:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,for awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It is on this energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,in this energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that we'll be talking today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It is within consciousness itself
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.66,0:08:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that all experience is being experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.66,0:08:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thereby to address ourselves directly
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.66,0:08:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,to the source and the place
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,of the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,will bring us to the capabilities
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,of precluding the sources of stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In doing this we'll be talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.20,0:08:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,a map of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.20,0:08:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,which we've referred to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,in these other talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a mathematical model.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Not purely mathematical
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but it is based upon energy fields,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:09:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and these energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,have been calibrated
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,as to their relative power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,here which are labeled
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.74,0:09:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,according to common human experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Easily understood
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and as you look at it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you will find that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,it's easily understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very bottom for instance
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,we have guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,which is in its form of self-hatred,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,a destructive negative emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that from guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.16,0:09:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the world is seen
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.16,0:09:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,as a place of suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.16,0:09:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Guiltiness has an energy field of 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,These are states that come close to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.16,0:09:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Death we calibrate at zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If we start with death at zero
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,then to be of a very high consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to become enlightened
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates out at 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.16,0:09:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Guilt you'll see in apathy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and grief and fear
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and desire and anger and pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.77,0:09:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All these negative energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:09:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,all have a negative
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.77,0:10:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,or a destructive direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.77,0:10:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll notice that their calibrations
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,are low in number.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance apathy at 50
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,has half the power of fear
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,which calibrates out at 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear at 100 has half the energy of courage
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.77,0:10:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,which calibrates out at 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.77,0:10:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Desire has half the energy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,of that state called neutral
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,or being detached.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can calibrate the energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and these can be reduplicated by anybody
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,using very common techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,for instance kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.77,0:10:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody in their own home can
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.77,0:10:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,verify themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.77,0:10:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the relative energies
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and the directions of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,These fields which go to the left
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,if you hold in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.77,0:10:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,a thought which is angry
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,a thought about something you regret
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,something you are sad about
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.77,0:10:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,or something you fear
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you press down on the person's arm
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you will see they instantly go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:10:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The cerebral hemispheres become desynchronized
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the acupuncture energy system
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.77,0:11:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,goes out of kilt
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.77,0:11:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and the person instantly goes to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The person instantly loses their power
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and their energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If we go above the level of courage
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll see the energy field now
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,which was in this direction
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,now goes neutral
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the needle swings to the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.77,0:11:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,By telling the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.77,0:11:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,by telling the truth about things
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.77,0:11:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,by moving towards that which is true
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy field now swings to the right
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,into that which is positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is positive
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,is that which supports and reinforces life
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that energy of aliveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It is aligned with the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the great beings of great wisdom
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.77,0:11:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,who have walked this earth
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.77,0:11:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,when we calibrate their energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,they run up into the 600s
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and the great avatars
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the great saviors of mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,their energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,run from the 700s on up into infinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So you might say the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:12:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,begins at this energy field of 200
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and expands ever upward
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,into an ever increasing lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,alignment with truth
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and health follows the same pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The farther we go up in our energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.90,0:12:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the more automatic becomes the health
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,until finally there is a joy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in the aliveness
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.90,0:12:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the exquisite pleasure of the body
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,which automatically becomes healthy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.90,0:12:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and it automatically heals its own diseases
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.90,0:12:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,because at an energy field of about 540
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the energy field of healing
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,healing automatically
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.93,0:12:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to take place in the body
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.93,0:12:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,at an energy field of 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So as we talk about stress
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it's obvious that we're going to be
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.60,0:12:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,looking at these conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,these pre-existing conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,within the consciousness of the person
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,which set the person up
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to experience life in a stressful way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:12:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious that a person
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,who is identified with this energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to experience a world
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,which is going to make them feel constantly guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious that a person who identifies
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,on this energy field here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,one of hopelessness and despair
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to experience the world as hopeless
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and all of life's experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.98,0:13:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,are going to be colored by that expectation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.18,0:13:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,As we move up to grief
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.18,0:13:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll see that the person who is full of regret
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and concern with loss in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to see this as a sad world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And if there is a God
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.18,0:13:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He would be a God who doesn't love you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,who doesn't care for you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and ignores you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.18,0:13:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As we move up to the energy field of fear
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,we see that coming out of the suppressed energy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.21,0:13:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,which has been held throughout life
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,held unconsciously
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.21,0:13:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,of fearfulness
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.21,0:13:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the preoccupation with anxiety about the future
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:14:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the person who is constantly worrying
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the world looks to that person
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,like a frightening place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.21,0:14:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The God of such a world
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,would then be punitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.46,0:14:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And so therefore
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,all that person's experience now
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is coming forth in the form of fright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.46,0:14:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who is always wanting
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,experiences this as a frustrating world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The angry person
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is always running into conflict and war.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The prideful person
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is always experiencing challenges
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore assumes a defensive posture.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's just a brief look at
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll be coming back to this map of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.46,0:14:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in greater detail
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and see how it operates
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in the automatic setting up
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and setting us up for stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We begin to suspect now
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,from that statement
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that one man's meat is another man's poison
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.75,0:14:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that the setup for stress then
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,is coming out of our own values.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.75,0:14:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming out of our own position about life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming out of the programs
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that we're holding operative
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,within our own consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And we begin to look now
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,for the source of stress
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,not in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.75,0:15:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but in what is it we are holding in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.75,0:15:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that assigns to a given event
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience of it as stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.68,0:15:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In looking at this
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll look now at some attitudes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,some ways of being with life
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.68,0:15:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that set us up for this kind of an experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll cite some examples
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,which are available to all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I had an in-law
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,for instance
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,who used to come out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.78,0:15:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and visit my house in the country
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.78,0:15:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,at the time I lived in the middle
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.78,0:15:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of a hundred acres of woods
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.78,0:15:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,thirty miles from New York City.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And there there was only stillness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.35,0:15:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact the only thing you could hear
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.35,0:15:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,was the rustling of the leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and the song of the birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And she was a somewhat elderly lady
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and she'd lived most of her life
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:15:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,in New York City
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you know on East 28th Street
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,around that area.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And she would hate to come out to the house
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.86,0:16:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and when she had to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,she would stay as briefly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact two or three days
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,was all she could stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And the peace and the silence
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,drove her crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And she just couldn't stand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.86,0:16:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And she couldn't wait to get back to the city
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.86,0:16:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,where she would sigh with relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And her apartment in the city
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.86,0:16:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you know faced the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And so from her open window
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,she could talk to everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,she could hear the hustle and bustle of the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And she felt secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So in the midst of
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you know it was mugger land
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the Lower East Side, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,all those areas of the city at that time
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,were ripe with muggings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.86,0:16:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So here she was
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you know in a situation
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,which another person might consider as stressful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of people might
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,consider that part of the city scary indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So what she experienced as security
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,being there in the throngs of people
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.86,0:16:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and the sound of the garbage cans in the morning
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.86,0:17:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and the garbage trucks
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.86,0:17:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,making their racket at 5 a.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to her was reassurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Being safe and secure
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.86,0:17:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,in the middle of 100 acres of woods
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.86,0:17:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to her was a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.89,0:17:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We look at the interesting experience then
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.89,0:17:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,of Devil's Island
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the French penal colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course this is well documented
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that when the French government
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,out of protest
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,coming from the humanism movement
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.89,0:17:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,out of social protest
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.89,0:17:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,closed this disgraceful colony
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,what happened was that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.92,0:17:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,they allowed the prisoners
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.92,0:17:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to go loose on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.92,0:17:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They released them from these animal cages.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Torture cages is what they really were.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the prisoners were now allowed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the freedom of the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The freedom to walk around at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And so what did the prisoners do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Much to the surprise of the authorities
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the prisoners had been in these cells for many years
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,at night they went back to their prison cells to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They felt frightened and lonely and insecure
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.11,0:18:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,even though for the first time in all these years
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,they had the freedom which they so ostensibly
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,had cried for and demanded over the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The sense of security then came from
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the feeling of being back in the jail cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.11,0:18:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So to some of us a jail cell would be
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.11,0:18:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the maximum threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.11,0:18:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing, no greater horror could befall us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.11,0:18:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And what have other people done in a prison cell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.11,0:18:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They've written prize winning novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They've written staggering pieces
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of literature.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Things written in jail cells and prisons
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,have changed the course and the history of mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.11,0:18:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,for better or for worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.11,0:18:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Adolf Hitler after all wrote Mein Kampf
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.11,0:18:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,while in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.11,0:18:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Another interesting example
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,in contrast to Devil's Island
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is exemplified by the movie Lost Horizon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll remember in that movie
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.14,0:19:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,which I remember well from childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it a number of times
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ronald Coleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The other passengers of the plane
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you know land in the Himalayas
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.14,0:19:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and they go through a pass
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and they come into Shangri-La
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,which represents a heavenly
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.14,0:19:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,almost a heavenly condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.14,0:19:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Its energy field is very high.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably up in the 600s.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A place of unconditional love
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,of unending bliss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And although Ronald Coleman was ready
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,for the experience and himself benefited God
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,greatly and expanded his own consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the other members of the passengers
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,took it in a different way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It was interesting to watch of six different people
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the six different reactions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.59,0:19:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A couple of them weren't quite ready
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.59,0:19:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,for the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.59,0:19:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Experienced it as sort of stress
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.59,0:19:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,due to its newness and its strangeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They felt stressed for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but then adjusted to it and accepted
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.46,0:20:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of a heavenly condition in their life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But several of the people were acutely
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,disturbed by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.46,0:20:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember the person who played
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ronald Coleman's brother in the movie
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,became almost paranoid and agitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.46,0:20:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Demanded to return to the real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And a person who was stranded there
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.46,0:20:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,from a previous plane accident
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,by that time had actually become paranoid
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,delusional and psychotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.46,0:20:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And so how it was experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,by these different people then
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,represented not a reaction to where
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,they were but a reaction to their own position.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And what they were talking about then
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,was not what's out there
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but their own level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.46,0:20:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember one time I was flying out of Ecuador
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and at that time there were only two planes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.26,0:20:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,a week going out of Ecuador.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.42,0:20:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I got there for the Thursday plane
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course I had reservations
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:21:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,many months in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When I got there the first thing they told me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,was that my name wasn't on the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.42,0:21:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And the next thing they said was that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.67,0:21:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the plane was not leaving on Thursday this week anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.67,0:21:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't leaving until Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, for some reason it just seemed to be humorous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed to be hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow when you're in Ecuador
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,at 10,000 feet altitude and above
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.02,0:21:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that the plane is going to be late
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.02,0:21:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in three days just doesn't mean a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.02,0:21:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody got upset about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.02,0:21:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And the interesting thing about the clock
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.02,0:21:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,in the airport which hung in the middle of the ceiling
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.57,0:21:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,was that the clock had stopped many years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.57,0:21:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and nobody had even bothered to fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.57,0:21:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see the expectation then
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,what is stressful coming out of this attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we had an easy going social attitude
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,in which precision within the material world
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.57,0:21:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't considered to be important.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.57,0:21:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Human values were of greater importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.57,0:21:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And because human values
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.57,0:22:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the convenience of the crew, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.57,0:22:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that was more important.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.57,0:22:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And so nobody seemed to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.57,0:22:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If that had happened in a different social setting
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.57,0:22:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,LaGuardia airport let's say
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.57,0:22:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that your Thursday plane is not leaving until Saturday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.57,0:22:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you would have experienced it as stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.57,0:22:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So the set and the setting, the expectation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.57,0:22:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the cultural attitude that you buy into.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.57,0:22:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In a different culture we buy a different attitude
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and in that culture
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.57,0:22:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,this event was not even experienced as stressful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.70,0:22:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.70,0:22:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,when I got there for the Saturday noon plane
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.70,0:22:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,it was due to leave at quarter to twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.70,0:22:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There was some kind of delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.70,0:22:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the only plane on the runway.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.70,0:22:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And the plane sat there
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.70,0:22:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and then suddenly it was twelve o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.70,0:22:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,At twelve o'clock they shut down for siesta.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.70,0:22:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So not only did the Thursday plane not leave until Saturday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.70,0:22:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,it didn't leave at quarter to twelve
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.70,0:22:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,it left at three o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.70,0:22:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the plane sat there
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.70,0:23:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,while everybody took a siesta.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.70,0:23:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,When the siesta was over
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.70,0:23:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody gathered their stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.70,0:23:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,got on the plane and away we went.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.70,0:23:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.70,0:23:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody sort of totally relaxed at ease
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.70,0:23:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,at peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be at peace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.73,0:23:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,with a three day delay in your plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.73,0:23:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So within these experiences that we have cited
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.73,0:23:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is the key
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.73,0:23:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the key to the understanding of stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.73,0:23:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Because when we talk about stress
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.73,0:23:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,what we're really talking about then
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.73,0:23:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is the experience of what is stressful within consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.73,0:23:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,To consider the body
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.73,0:23:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,as part of a stress response
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.73,0:23:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is a very late reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.73,0:23:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The body is only responding
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.30,0:23:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to what is held in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.30,0:23:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The body is only responding to that which is held in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.30,0:23:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And so by altering what we hold in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.30,0:23:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,our expectations, our way of being with life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.30,0:23:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,we can preclude the development of stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.30,0:23:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have to go to a relaxation program
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.30,0:23:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to handle the stress
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.30,0:24:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of the plane being three days late.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.30,0:24:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have to go to some kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.30,0:24:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,coronary exercise program
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.30,0:24:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to protect my heart from stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.30,0:24:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't any stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.30,0:24:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently, the real approach to stress then
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.30,0:24:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is to prevent it in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.30,0:24:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,To preclude it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.30,0:24:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,To understand how it arises
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.30,0:24:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and where it arises.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.30,0:24:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So our first understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.30,0:24:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and I think it's rather obvious by now
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.30,0:24:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,from the examples we've given
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.69,0:24:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,is that the source of what we experience as stress
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.69,0:24:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,is within ourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.69,0:24:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It does not exist in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.69,0:24:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't exist in plane schedules.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.69,0:24:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't exist in prison cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.69,0:24:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nowhere does it exist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.69,0:24:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,except within our own consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.69,0:24:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we need to go back then to this map
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.69,0:24:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to this field of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.69,0:24:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and understand it a little bit more closely
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.69,0:24:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and then our awareness of this subject
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.69,0:24:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,will advance rather rapidly
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.69,0:24:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,because what we're talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.69,0:24:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,is really easy to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.69,0:24:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something you really know already.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.69,0:25:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that we're going to bring it into awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.23,0:25:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We said that these energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.23,0:25:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,on the bottom which are
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.23,0:25:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you might say adverse to life
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.23,0:25:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,destructive of life
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.23,0:25:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,we would call them stress
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.23,0:25:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,just by their own nature
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.23,0:25:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that the energy field indicates a stressful direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.23,0:25:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That we move above it to neutral
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.23,0:25:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,we move in a positive direction
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.23,0:25:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to that which is unstressful.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.23,0:25:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So that Shangri-La would be up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.23,0:25:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All things are experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.23,0:25:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,in their beauty and perfection
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.23,0:25:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the oneness of life
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.23,0:25:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the unconditional love
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.23,0:25:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and the lovingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.23,0:25:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So out of these energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.74,0:25:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,out of these energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.74,0:25:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,which are calibrated as to their relative power
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.74,0:25:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to the right of it we see
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.74,0:25:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the emotions that come out of that position
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.74,0:25:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that way of being with life.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.74,0:25:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We see that those who are prone to guiltiness
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.74,0:25:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,for instance
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.74,0:25:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the emotion is one of self-hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.74,0:25:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The experience of life is that it is destructive
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.74,0:26:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and as we said
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.74,0:26:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,what they see is a world of suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.74,0:26:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They see a world of suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.74,0:26:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who is holding this position
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.84,0:26:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,of apathy about life
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.84,0:26:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the emotion is one of hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.84,0:26:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Life is hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.84,0:26:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Life is despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.84,0:26:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a loss of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.84,0:26:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is seen as hopeless
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.84,0:26:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and the god of such a world is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.84,0:26:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If we move out of apathy
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.58,0:26:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,if we pour enough energy into a person in apathy
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.58,0:26:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,we can get them up to grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.58,0:26:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Grief is a state in which you can express emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.58,0:26:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It has a certain biologic purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.58,0:26:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The expression of grief
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.58,0:26:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,like the crying of the child brings the mother
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.58,0:26:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,has a certain biologic purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.58,0:26:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who are in that energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.58,0:26:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,are looking to the past
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.58,0:26:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and they see their life
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.58,0:26:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,filled with regret and loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.58,0:26:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They become dispirited.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.58,0:26:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They experience this as a sad world
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.58,0:27:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and the god of that world ignores you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.58,0:27:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We said that the person who is coming from
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.58,0:27:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the suppressed energy field of fear
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.58,0:27:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,is looking to life
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.58,0:27:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,filled with worry and anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.58,0:27:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They experience life as frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.18,0:27:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what is life?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.18,0:27:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a view of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.18,0:27:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The view of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.18,0:27:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.18,0:27:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the thing in and of itself?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.18,0:27:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it coming out of the event?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.18,0:27:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We see then that these fields of energy
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.18,0:27:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,are really portholes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.18,0:27:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They are ways in which we see the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.18,0:27:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the color of the glasses that we put on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.18,0:27:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If we put on gray glasses coming out of grief
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.18,0:27:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,everything looks sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.18,0:27:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A person walking down the street
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.73,0:27:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,who is coming from this energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.73,0:27:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,sees everything on the street as hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.73,0:27:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks at man and man's conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.73,0:27:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He opens the paper and he sees hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.73,0:27:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Man's condition is hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.73,0:27:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,As he walks down the street
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.73,0:28:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,he looks at the old people
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.73,0:28:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and he sees how hopeless their condition is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.73,0:28:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks at the children
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.73,0:28:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and he sees how hopeless it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.73,0:28:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They are going to have to grow up
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.73,0:28:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,in a world of hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.73,0:28:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who is sad
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.73,0:28:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,walks down the street
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.73,0:28:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and they literally experience
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.73,0:28:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,their perception is one of sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.73,0:28:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,When they open the newspaper
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.73,0:28:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,they see all that there is
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.73,0:28:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to be sad about in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.73,0:28:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,As they walk down the street
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.73,0:28:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,they see the sadness of man's condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.73,0:28:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They see the trash on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.73,0:28:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They look at the old people
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.73,0:28:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and they think how sad,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.73,0:28:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,how sad aging is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.73,0:28:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They look at the children
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.73,0:28:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and they feel sorry for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.73,0:28:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They think how sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.73,0:28:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They pity the children,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.73,0:28:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the kind of a world
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.73,0:28:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,they are going to have to grow up in.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.73,0:28:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the pain of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.73,0:28:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They are holding so much pain
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.73,0:28:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that the pity expresses itself now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.73,0:28:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How sad for these children.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.73,0:28:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who is coming from
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.53,0:28:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy field of fear
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.53,0:28:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,sees and experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.53,0:28:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and creates in his world
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.53,0:28:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience of that which is fearful.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.53,0:29:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So the person opens the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.53,0:29:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He reads the same newspaper
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.53,0:29:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and he sees how fearful this world is.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.53,0:29:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Killings and murder
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.53,0:29:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and muggings and war and bombings.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.53,0:29:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He walks down the street
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.17,0:29:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and he sees how frightening is the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.17,0:29:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He sees the, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.17,0:29:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the chance for accidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.17,0:29:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He sees people can twist their
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.17,0:29:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,ankle on the curb.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.17,0:29:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be warning signs all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.17,0:29:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who sees this
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.17,0:29:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,as a frightening world
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.17,0:29:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,double locks everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.17,0:29:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I know people
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.17,0:29:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,who double lock their car
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.17,0:29:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,within their own double lock garage,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.17,0:29:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,within their own double lock yard
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.17,0:29:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,in an area which has never had a robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.17,0:29:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the fear then is coming from within
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.46,0:29:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and it projects onto the world
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.46,0:29:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,a frightening appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.46,0:29:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have got fear colored glasses,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.46,0:29:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,everything looks like fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.46,0:29:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you search for God,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.46,0:29:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you would see a fearful God, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.46,0:29:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The God of a frightening world
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.46,0:29:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is someone to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.46,0:30:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who moves up in the street
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.19,0:30:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,into a higher energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.19,0:30:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,of desiringness and wantingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.19,0:30:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,often this comes about merely by education.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.19,0:30:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say people at the bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.19,0:30:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,into hopelessness through television,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.19,0:30:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole third world,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.19,0:30:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,segments of the lowest socioeconomic groups
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.19,0:30:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,in our society in the last 20 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.19,0:30:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,or 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.19,0:30:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,When television came along,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.19,0:30:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,began to see that which other people have.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.22,0:30:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What came up out of that was desire, desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.38,0:30:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is felt in the emotional field then,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.38,0:30:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,as wanting and craving.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.38,0:30:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This expresses itself in its fullest
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.38,0:30:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in the addictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.38,0:30:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The process going on in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.38,0:30:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is one of entrapment
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.38,0:30:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,because once you desire something,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.38,0:30:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you begin to want it,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.38,0:30:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you then experience this world as frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.38,0:30:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So the stress then that this person experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.38,0:30:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is the endless frustration
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.38,0:30:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,because coming out of that sort of
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.38,0:30:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,solar plexus endless wantingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.38,0:31:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the person who is never satisfied,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.38,0:31:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what they get.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.38,0:31:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They're always wanting something more.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.38,0:31:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If they get you to concede to their wishes,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.38,0:31:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,they bring up more wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.38,0:31:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like it's an endless control
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.38,0:31:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that they want over life.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.38,0:31:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They see this as a very frustrating world
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.38,0:31:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and so as they walk down the street,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.38,0:31:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,they see all the things they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.38,0:31:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They see the cars that they want,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.38,0:31:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,they see the kind of appearance,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.38,0:31:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,they see the appurtenances that they want,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.38,0:31:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,they see the addresses that they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.38,0:31:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,As they open the newspaper,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.38,0:31:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,they're seeing all the things that they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.38,0:31:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They want to change the world they want to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.38,0:31:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So this endless addiction to getting this
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.74,0:31:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,then creates an endless stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.74,0:31:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This stress, as you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.74,0:31:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is coming from within the self.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.74,0:31:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no refusal on the part of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.74,0:31:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to come to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.74,0:31:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your endless desiringness for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.44,0:31:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who, out of this frustration then,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.44,0:31:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,moves up to anger,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.44,0:32:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to experience this as an angry world.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.44,0:32:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They're full of resentment,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.44,0:32:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,they're boiling over with hate and grievance.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.44,0:32:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens with a person like this
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.44,0:32:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is the suppressed energy now of the angriness
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.44,0:32:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is ready to spill forth in any event.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.44,0:32:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They see this world as competitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.44,0:32:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So to this person,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.44,0:32:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the kind of glasses they're wearing,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.44,0:32:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,they're wearing angry glasses,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.44,0:32:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,when they open the newspaper,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.54,0:32:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,their stomach churns with wrath and indignation
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.54,0:32:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and anger over the events that they're reading about.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.54,0:32:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,As they walk down the street,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.70,0:32:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,they see many things to be angry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.70,0:32:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All the conditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.70,0:32:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the conditions of the street signs,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.70,0:32:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the conditions of the street,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.70,0:32:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the newspapers there on the street now make them angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.70,0:32:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They look at the children, that makes them angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.70,0:32:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They look at the old folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.70,0:32:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They think of their conditions and they become angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.70,0:32:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So they live in a world of injustice,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.70,0:32:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,indignation,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.70,0:32:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,a competitive world,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.70,0:33:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,if they have a used car lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.70,0:33:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, sell used cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.70,0:33:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If somebody else opens another used car lot down the street,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.70,0:33:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,they consider this competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.70,0:33:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They look at it like lose,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.70,0:33:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,they're going to lose
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.70,0:33:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,because these people live in a win-lose world.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.70,0:33:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, the stomach is always tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.70,0:33:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They haven't moved up to a higher level of harmony and cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.70,0:33:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently, they don't realize
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.86,0:33:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that the more used car lots on the street,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.86,0:33:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the better for business.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.86,0:33:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They would see it as competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.86,0:33:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So the world becomes a threatening place.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.86,0:33:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The god of that kind of a universe
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.86,0:33:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,would be the god of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.02,0:33:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So out of this angriness,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.02,0:33:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,these are warlike people ready for combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.02,0:33:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They have a chip on their shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.02,0:33:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That anger is ready to burst forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.69,0:33:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is very stressful then.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.69,0:33:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.69,0:33:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the suppressed anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.69,0:33:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So somebody should back into their fender in the parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.69,0:33:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Up comes the anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.69,0:33:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Up comes the cursing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.69,0:34:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Up comes the threat of the lawsuit,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.69,0:34:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the angriness.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.69,0:34:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If a person can move up to pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.88,0:34:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's a lot of energy in pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.88,0:34:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you see these are all negative destructive emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.88,0:34:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Pride, although we like to think of it as constructive,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.88,0:34:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,in essence it is really destructive.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.88,0:34:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.88,0:34:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Because pride is denial.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.88,0:34:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Its expression is really one of arrogance and contempt.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.88,0:34:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And because the process going on in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.88,0:34:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is one of inflation.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.88,0:34:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The prideful person then becomes very polarized in his positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.88,0:34:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's prideful like the angry person.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.88,0:34:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,His position is right and they live in a world of right and wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.88,0:34:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a world of win-lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.88,0:34:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore there is always a stress going on within that person
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.88,0:34:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,because they see all relationships and interactions and transactions
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.88,0:34:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,in terms of win-lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.88,0:34:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And the win-lose is about status.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.88,0:34:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.88,0:34:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,ownership.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.88,0:35:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So that person, when he reads the newspaper,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.23,0:35:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is seeing the status of all that is involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.23,0:35:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The status of the people that is being written about.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.23,0:35:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When he walks down the street, he sees nothing but symbols of status.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.23,0:35:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The labels on clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.23,0:35:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the addresses,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.23,0:35:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,all these things about life now become status.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.23,0:35:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're very interested in who you are
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.23,0:35:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,from a status viewpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.23,0:35:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all vulnerable positions as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.23,0:35:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all positions
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.23,0:35:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of victim really
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.23,0:35:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,because all of these positions below the level of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.23,0:35:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,project the source of happiness as outside yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.23,0:35:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It gives your power away.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.23,0:35:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It says the source of meaning,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.23,0:35:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the source of happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.23,0:35:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the source of value is something outside myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.23,0:35:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's somewhere out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.23,0:35:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming from lack because it's saying if it's out there
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.23,0:35:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it's something I have to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.23,0:35:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's something I have to get it means I lack it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.23,0:35:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It means something could stand in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.23,0:36:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And so to live in that kind of a world is to always live in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.23,0:36:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Always live under threat
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.23,0:36:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,because something outside of yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.23,0:36:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you can be blocked from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.23,0:36:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.23,0:36:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The world of victimhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.23,0:36:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Victimhood because we've given away our power to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.23,0:36:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We say that the source of happiness is out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.23,0:36:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The source of stress is out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.36,0:36:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no hope for relieving stress by changing the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.36,0:36:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.36,0:36:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Because stress doesn't exist in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.36,0:36:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Stress is an inexperience within consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.36,0:36:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you can change the world to relieve stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.36,0:36:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What can we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.71,0:36:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We can own, begin to own the truth about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.71,0:36:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to have the courage to look at the facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.71,0:36:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute we do that we change the energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.71,0:36:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We see that the needle now goes to neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.71,0:36:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We're coming out of destructive on our way into positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.71,0:36:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,When we're willing to face something,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.35,0:36:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,face the facts,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.35,0:36:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to face, cope and handle it,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.35,0:37:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens is we become re-empowered.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.35,0:37:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That means we begin to own back the power to ourself now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.35,0:37:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're coming closer to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.96,0:37:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And a prisoner who's on the level of courage,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.96,0:37:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,what kind of a world does that person see?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.96,0:37:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They see a world of challenge, of growth and of opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.96,0:37:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,An exciting, fun world.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.96,0:37:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A place where you're glad to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.96,0:37:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And so that same person opens the newspaper
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.96,0:37:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and he sees all the tremendous opportunities
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.96,0:37:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,for man to move into and solve and resolve this problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.96,0:37:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And he has all kinds of problems,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.96,0:37:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, solving things in his own mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.96,0:37:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He just wishes he could try.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.96,0:37:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So it becomes an exciting world then of opportunity and growth,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.96,0:37:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,which he begins to ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.96,0:37:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,where can I fit in?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.96,0:37:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Where can I start expressing myself
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.96,0:37:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and experiencing some of these opportunities?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.96,0:37:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of a God that he experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.96,0:37:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,of this world of opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.96,0:37:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is a God of open-mindedness.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.96,0:37:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So the open mind now begins to change,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.96,0:38:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,obviously, that which is stressful.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.96,0:38:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is stressful down here
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.96,0:38:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes perhaps an object of curiosity
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.96,0:38:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and an opportunity for growth to a person here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.96,0:38:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving up to the next energy field we call neutral,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.57,0:38:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,where the energy calibrates out at 250.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.57,0:38:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how much more power we have
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.57,0:38:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,than these positions up down below.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.57,0:38:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only more power, but we see that
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.57,0:38:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that power is now being used in a constructive,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.57,0:38:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,positive direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.57,0:38:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though down here our antenna
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.57,0:38:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is tuned to the negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.57,0:38:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it's turned to neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.57,0:38:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we're tuning our antenna to the positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.57,0:38:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We begin to experience life in a positive direction
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.57,0:38:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,because we are the experiencer.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.57,0:38:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The experiencer is not out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.57,0:38:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It is within our own consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.57,0:38:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That person is willing to let go
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.57,0:38:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of their positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.57,0:38:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of the positions that make this person
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.57,0:38:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and person's life hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.57,0:38:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the sense of being always defensive
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.57,0:38:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,due to his pridefulness, his importance,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.57,0:39:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the sense of always being right,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.57,0:39:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the position of either the atheist
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.57,0:39:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,or the bigot or the zealot
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.57,0:39:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that leads to all the religious wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.57,0:39:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, my position is right,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.57,0:39:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore your position is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.14,0:39:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to let that go,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.14,0:39:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the person becomes somewhat unattached.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.14,0:39:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They begin to transcend their vulnerability to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.14,0:39:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The process going on in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.14,0:39:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,is that they're released.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.14,0:39:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The world begins to look
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.14,0:39:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,okay to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.14,0:39:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The god of such a world now
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.14,0:39:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is the god of freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.27,0:39:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that okayness expressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.27,0:39:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, a person on this level,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.27,0:39:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,on the way to a job interview,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.27,0:39:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,would say, you know, if I get this job
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.27,0:39:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.27,0:39:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I don't, that's okay too
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.27,0:39:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,because there's other job opportunities
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.27,0:39:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I would really like to look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.27,0:39:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And so he's not stuck, he hasn't put his
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.27,0:39:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,survival on any one particular thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.27,0:39:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Beginning to own
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.27,0:39:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that the power is within myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.27,0:39:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,As we move into willingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.27,0:40:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,we add something else now
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.27,0:40:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,from the process of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.27,0:40:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We add intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.27,0:40:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It means a yes-ness, a joining,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.27,0:40:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,an alignment, an agreement with life.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.27,0:40:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And such a person
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.43,0:40:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to see the world
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.43,0:40:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,as friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.43,0:40:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So when these people walk down the street,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.43,0:40:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the god of that kind of a world
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.43,0:40:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,would become promising and hopeful.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.43,0:40:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Their experience now
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.43,0:40:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,in the newspaper
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.43,0:40:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,is they begin to open it up
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.43,0:40:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and they see all the evidences
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.43,0:40:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,of man's cooperation,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.43,0:40:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,man's struggle to solve its own problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.43,0:40:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They see what this person sees as destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.43,0:40:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,as merely the process,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.43,0:40:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the working out of the balance of forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.43,0:40:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They begin to see
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.43,0:40:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,a friendlier world.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.43,0:40:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And so when they walk down the street
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.43,0:40:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,they see a friendly look.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.43,0:40:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You see their perception has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.43,0:40:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They see the friendliness of old people.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.43,0:40:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Old people who no longer have to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.43,0:40:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world, you know, very often
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.43,0:40:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,are much more open to be friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.43,0:40:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Simple to walk up to most older people
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.43,0:41:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and strike up a conversation instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.43,0:41:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't look at you with that paranoid distrust
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.43,0:41:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,or size you up and down to see where you stand
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.43,0:41:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,in a competitive, prideful world.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.43,0:41:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They begin to see
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.85,0:41:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the old people as friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.85,0:41:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They see the friendliness of the young children.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.85,0:41:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They become conscious of the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.85,0:41:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that children are friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.85,0:41:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy to strike up a relationship with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.01,0:41:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And so moving up
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.01,0:41:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,into acceptance then,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.01,0:41:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you really begin to accept that one
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.01,0:41:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,is the source of one's own experience of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.01,0:41:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,As we've said in other talks,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.01,0:41:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,a person who's reached
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.01,0:41:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,this level of awareness,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.01,0:41:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,who's owned the power back over his own life,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.01,0:41:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,realizes that no matter where you put him,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.01,0:41:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,he's going to somehow make do.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.01,0:41:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You put him on a desert island,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.01,0:41:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you come back a year later,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.01,0:41:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you know he's carving coconuts,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.01,0:41:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's got a tree house.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.04,0:41:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You put him in a jail cell,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.04,0:41:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll write a novel,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.04,0:41:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,or he'll sit cross-legged and go into meditation,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.04,0:41:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,or he'll become a jailhouse lawyer
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.04,0:41:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and get a law degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.04,0:41:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The power to create
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.04,0:42:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,my experience of life is within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.04,0:42:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The person has re-owned
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.04,0:42:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,their own power.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.04,0:42:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently, such a God,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.04,0:42:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the God of that kind of a world
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.04,0:42:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and universe of experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.04,0:42:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes not only promising and hopeful,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.04,0:42:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but merciful.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.04,0:42:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A merciful God no longer to be feared.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.04,0:42:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That person is adequate and confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.04,0:42:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We want that kind of a person
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.04,0:42:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to go out after the big contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.04,0:42:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So that person is able to accept
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.04,0:42:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the upside and the downside
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.04,0:42:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and the realities of life
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.04,0:42:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and can accept their own limitations.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.04,0:42:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, a person coming out of pride
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.04,0:42:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,can't accept that they are limited
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.04,0:42:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and they have to come from a prideful,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.04,0:42:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,macho position.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.42,0:42:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The person in acceptance,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.42,0:42:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,when the company says,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.42,0:42:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd like you to go to Venezuela
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.42,0:42:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and close such and such a deal,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.58,0:42:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,a person who is adequate and confident
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.58,0:42:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,could say, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.58,0:42:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get along with that company
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.58,0:42:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't get along with that particular man.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.58,0:42:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I do much better in Belgium.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.58,0:42:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I can sell twice as much in Belgium.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.58,0:43:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you let Jim go down to Venezuela?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.58,0:43:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness then to accept
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.58,0:43:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,how the world works.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.58,0:43:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't get into indignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.58,0:43:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the IRS has its way
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.58,0:43:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,of being in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.58,0:43:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They get out of right and wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.58,0:43:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They just accept that's how it is in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.58,0:43:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and they go with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.58,0:43:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the beginning of transformation
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.58,0:43:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness then
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.58,0:43:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,is the real realization
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.58,0:43:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that I am the source
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.58,0:43:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore the world begins to look
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.58,0:43:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,harmonious and merciful.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.16,0:43:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That empowerment moves a person up then
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.16,0:43:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to the next energy field of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.16,0:43:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we mean by love?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.16,0:43:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't mean the sentimental emotionalism
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.16,0:43:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that comes out of the solar plexus attachment
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.16,0:43:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,of what Hollywood calls love.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.16,0:43:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That emotionalism
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.16,0:43:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,coming out of a possessive ownership
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.16,0:43:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,of the other person
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.16,0:43:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and that back and forth control.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.16,0:43:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The subtle power struggles
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.16,0:43:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.16,0:44:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That enamored coming out of a song
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.16,0:44:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that if you leave me I'll die kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.16,0:44:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If you leave me I will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.32,0:44:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all coming out of an attachment
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.32,0:44:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,which has nothing to do with love.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.32,0:44:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking about here unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.32,0:44:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A way of being with life
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.32,0:44:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that nurtures, supports
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.32,0:44:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,which is of its own nature forgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.32,0:44:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the beginning of the revelation
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.32,0:44:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,of some of the truth of life
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.32,0:44:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,because within the brain
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.32,0:44:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,there's the release of endorphins.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.32,0:44:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Endorphins allow
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.32,0:44:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,a certain inner state
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.32,0:44:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to occur, a way of being with oneself
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.32,0:44:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and one's body and the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.32,0:44:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And now the world
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.32,0:44:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,starts to appear loving.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.32,0:44:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So that person walks down the street
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.32,0:44:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,feeling somewhat mellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.32,0:44:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They see the lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.32,0:44:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that really goes on
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.32,0:44:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,underneath the apparent trivialities
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.32,0:44:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,they really see the lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.32,0:44:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that holds all of mankind together.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.32,0:44:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They're moving into a higher energy field.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.32,0:44:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing life as harmonious
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.86,0:44:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,seeing life as loving
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.86,0:44:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you can see how much stress now
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.86,0:45:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,this person is vulnerable to
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.86,0:45:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,because they are coming
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.86,0:45:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,from a forgivingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.86,0:45:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That forgivingness
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.41,0:45:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the coming out of the intention
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.41,0:45:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,of that feel which you choose for yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.41,0:45:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,we call it lovingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.41,0:45:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that the person
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.41,0:45:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,coming out of lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.41,0:45:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,is loving towards all things
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.41,0:45:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.41,0:45:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Loving towards mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.41,0:45:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Loving and nurturing towards oneself.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.41,0:45:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the difference
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.41,0:45:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,in how these people would view themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.41,0:45:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The harshness
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.41,0:45:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,of the perfectionist
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.41,0:45:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,puts him always at stress
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.41,0:45:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,with his own human nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.41,0:45:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The unforgivingness
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.41,0:45:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the capacity to judge and condemn
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.41,0:45:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the self-hatred and guilt
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.41,0:45:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,means for that person
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.41,0:45:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,to breathe in and out
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.41,0:45:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,is to be in a state of stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.41,0:45:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If he gets up late
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.41,0:45:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,he blames himself for getting up late.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.41,0:45:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The stress is there
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.41,0:45:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,coming out of the perfectionism
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.41,0:45:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the inflexibility
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.41,0:46:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the capacity for self-condemnation.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.41,0:46:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the stress you see
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.41,0:46:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,is internally generated.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.41,0:46:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The open-minded person
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.41,0:46:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that starts to become more easy with himself
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.41,0:46:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to become accepting
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.41,0:46:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,of his own humaneness.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.41,0:46:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And as we move up to forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.41,0:46:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,we have that mental attitude
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.41,0:46:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,of the readiness
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.41,0:46:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,to allow the humaneness
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.41,0:46:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and when we do that
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.41,0:46:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,we allow our own humaneness.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.92,0:46:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We move up then
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.92,0:46:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to an even higher energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.92,0:46:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of joyfulness
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.92,0:46:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,which is approaching the beginning awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.92,0:46:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of the reality of that
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.92,0:46:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,in which you really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.92,0:46:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That you are not the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.92,0:46:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you are the experiencer.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.92,0:46:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not at the effect of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.92,0:46:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you are the one that is determining
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.92,0:46:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the way you experience it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.92,0:46:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you develop a certain inner serenity
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.92,0:46:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and out of this
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.92,0:46:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,passion towards all of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.92,0:46:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The beginning to see the incredible
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.92,0:46:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,beauty and perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.92,0:46:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The experiencing of the oneness
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.92,0:47:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and the unity of all life.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.92,0:47:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And so that one
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.92,0:47:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so that person opens the newspaper
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.92,0:47:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you see and experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.92,0:47:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the totality of man's lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.92,0:47:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,seeing that despite
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.92,0:47:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,his humaneness which is what is making
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.92,0:47:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,all the articles appear
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.92,0:47:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,in the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.92,0:47:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The experience of that onward movement
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.92,0:47:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the expression of the onward movement
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.92,0:47:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and evolution of man's consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.92,0:47:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And so when that person walks down
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.24,0:47:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the same street
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.24,0:47:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,he experiences only
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.24,0:47:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the incredible beauty of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.24,0:47:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Experiencing the beauty of life
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.24,0:47:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,in all its magnificent expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.24,0:47:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,As though you see
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.24,0:47:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,a rose in the middle of its unfoldingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.24,0:47:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,See the perfectionist
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.24,0:47:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,would look at the half unfolded rose
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.24,0:47:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and say I don't want that
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.24,0:47:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that's an imperfect rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.75,0:47:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The person on this level
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.75,0:47:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,sees the perfection of the evolution of life
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.75,0:47:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,itself and sees all of life
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.75,0:47:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,as that half unfolded rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.75,0:47:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That in one second
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.75,0:48:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,there is only a cross section
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.75,0:48:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but projects forward in time
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.75,0:48:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and sees the unfoldingness
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.75,0:48:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and the incredible beauty and precision
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.75,0:48:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and becomes aware
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.75,0:48:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,inwardly of the inner sacredness
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.75,0:48:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of all life.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.90,0:48:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious then as we talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.90,0:48:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,these energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.90,0:48:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,as these levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.90,0:48:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that they are determining
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.90,0:48:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,how we experience life.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.90,0:48:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They are determining
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.90,0:48:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,what kind of a God we think
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.90,0:48:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,exists in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.90,0:48:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,These energy fields are determining
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.90,0:48:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the kind of emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.90,0:48:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,which we are expressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.90,0:48:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All of this expressing
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.90,0:48:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,a process going on
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.90,0:48:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,within consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.03,0:48:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It certainly is very clear to us now
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.03,0:48:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.03,0:48:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,out there
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.03,0:48:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that has the power
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.03,0:48:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to create stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.03,0:48:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That we ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.03,0:48:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,are the creators of stress
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.03,0:48:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,by the positions
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.03,0:49:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,by our attitudes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.16,0:49:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious that the open minded
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.16,0:49:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,easy going person
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.16,0:49:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't experience stress
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.16,0:49:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,when somebody backs into his fender
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.18,0:49:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,in the parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.18,0:49:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens, you've experienced it yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.18,0:49:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're in a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.18,0:49:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what is stressful in one mood
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.18,0:49:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is not stressful in another.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.44,0:49:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I came out myself
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.44,0:49:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,one day to the parking lot
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.57,0:49:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and there was somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.57,0:49:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,who was the only offender.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.57,0:49:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And the person was very upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.57,0:49:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And frankly my only concern
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.57,0:49:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,was the upsetness of this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.57,0:49:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And I kept telling them
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.57,0:49:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nothing to be upset about.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.57,0:49:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean it's only offender.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.57,0:49:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We both got insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.57,0:49:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.57,0:49:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a little nuisance
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.76,0:49:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you've got to take your car
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.76,0:49:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to the body shop and get it fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.76,0:49:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's really no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.76,0:49:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was the getting
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.76,0:49:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and the desire to heal that upset
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.76,0:49:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that arose in the field
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.76,0:50:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,of my own consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.34,0:50:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So whether it's something
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.34,0:50:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that sends you into self pity
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.34,0:50:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,about what an unjust world this is
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.34,0:50:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that people back into your fender.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.34,0:50:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you want to punch the guy
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.34,0:50:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,in the nose because you've got
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.34,0:50:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,so much anger in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.34,0:50:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you're concerned
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.34,0:50:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,in just handling the facts involved
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.34,0:50:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,with no particular feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.34,0:50:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The detached person would just handle
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.53,0:50:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,this with no particular feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.53,0:50:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They just want to support life
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.53,0:50:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and relieve their anxiety and their fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.53,0:50:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All of that you see is coming out
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.53,0:50:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,of who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.53,0:50:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't exist in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.53,0:50:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A dented fender therefore has no power
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.53,0:50:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,over your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.53,0:50:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We've just taken its power away.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.53,0:50:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We've just owned it back within ourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.53,0:50:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And we've just precluded
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.53,0:50:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the sources of stress
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.53,0:50:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,by just the realization
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.53,0:50:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,about what we've talked about thus far.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.53,0:50:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A certain state of inner peace then
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.53,0:50:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically comes up
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.53,0:50:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,of our willingness to give up
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.53,0:50:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,certain positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.53,0:51:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Our willingness to give up judging others.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.53,0:51:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Making them wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.53,0:51:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Our willingness then to come from
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.53,0:51:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,a forgiving understanding position.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.53,0:51:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, right or wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.53,0:51:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't really solve anything, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.53,0:51:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to accept people
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.53,0:51:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,as they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.53,0:51:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If we come from this position here
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.53,0:51:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,making them wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.53,0:51:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,we live in a world of win-lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.53,0:51:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The people at the bottom here
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.53,0:51:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,are coming from a world
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.53,0:51:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,of lose-lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.53,0:51:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a world where I lose
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.53,0:51:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and the company loses.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.53,0:51:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,In the middle of the
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.53,0:51:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,energy field here
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.53,0:51:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,we come from positions
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.53,0:51:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,which result in
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.53,0:51:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,win-lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.88,0:51:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It means if I win, you lose, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.88,0:51:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's stressful
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.88,0:51:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,by the context.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.88,0:51:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's stressful in the very way
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.88,0:51:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.88,0:51:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Because even if you win
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.88,0:51:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to go through the anxiety of losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.88,0:51:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So even winning doesn't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.88,0:51:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even winning doesn't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.88,0:52:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that people, for instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.07,0:52:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,who say, I want to have a lot of money
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.07,0:52:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens to them
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.07,0:52:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,when you give them a lot of money?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.07,0:52:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, some interesting research has been done
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.07,0:52:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,on people who win
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.07,0:52:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,millions of dollars
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.07,0:52:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,in big lotteries and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.07,0:52:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We find out that within five years
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.07,0:52:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,a five-year follow-up
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.07,0:52:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that the degree of happiness in this group of people
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.07,0:52:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,was dismal.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.07,0:52:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The suicide rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.07,0:52:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the divorce rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.07,0:52:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the sickness rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.26,0:52:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the addiction to drugs
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.26,0:52:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,had risen spectacularly in these people
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.26,0:52:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,who had gotten ostensibly
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.26,0:52:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the very thing they wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.26,0:52:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason they played the lottery
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.26,0:52:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,was to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.26,0:52:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The win-lose game, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.26,0:52:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,because if you structure things as win-lose
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.26,0:52:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,then to win in itself
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.26,0:52:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,means to defeat others.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.26,0:52:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,To defeat others brings up what?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.26,0:52:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Brings up guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.26,0:52:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you can't even be happy in winning
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.26,0:52:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,or losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.26,0:52:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In the win-lose context,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.26,0:53:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,if I win, then you are defeated
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.26,0:53:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have to put up with the guilt of that defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.26,0:53:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If I win in competition,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.26,0:53:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I then have to go into fear
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.26,0:53:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,because in competition
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.26,0:53:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I then expect retaliation
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.26,0:53:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,from my enemy, from my opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.26,0:53:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So I may have defeated him this time
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.26,0:53:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but now I worry whether his friends
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.26,0:53:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,are out to get me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.26,0:53:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And so these are really sort of paranoid positions,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.26,0:53:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,depressed, paranoid positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.87,0:53:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,At the bottom of the box,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.87,0:53:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,that is a hopeless, sinful world.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.87,0:53:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In the middle,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.97,0:53:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,we have win-lose with the anxiety,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.97,0:53:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the stress that automatically comes out of
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.97,0:53:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,a win-lose position.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.61,0:53:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,As we move towards the top of the box,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.61,0:53:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,those positions of great success
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.61,0:53:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and power in the world automatically
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.61,0:53:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,come to those who think in terms of
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.61,0:53:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,win-win.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.70,0:53:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they are coming from that position,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.70,0:53:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,they then set up
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.70,0:53:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,within their own mind
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.70,0:53:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,a way of being in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.70,0:53:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and a way for others to be in their life
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.70,0:53:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and automatically win-win.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.28,0:54:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of stress then
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.28,0:54:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,does the person experience
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.28,0:54:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,who is setting up everything
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.28,0:54:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,as win-win?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.30,0:54:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The person wins if they come over to your house
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.30,0:54:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and they win if they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.30,0:54:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If they come over to your house,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.30,0:54:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,what you hold is how much
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.30,0:54:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to enjoy their friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.30,0:54:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and their presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.30,0:54:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And at the same time you let them know
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.37,0:54:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,if you can't make it, that's great
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.37,0:54:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,because I've got a book I'm working on
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.37,0:54:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can use the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.37,0:54:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The other person in your life now
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.37,0:54:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,wins either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.37,0:54:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If they come for dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.37,0:54:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,you're delighted with their presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.37,0:54:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If they don't come for dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.37,0:54:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,you've given them the free time
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.37,0:54:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,to do something that you know
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.37,0:54:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,will enhance their life.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.37,0:54:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So everybody wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.37,0:54:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So to hold all one's positions
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.37,0:54:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,in business for instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.37,0:54:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,in a situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.37,0:54:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,you can imagine how successful it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.37,0:54:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If my position is,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.37,0:54:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the marketer wins,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.37,0:55:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the magazine wins,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.37,0:55:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,all of our bank accounts win,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.37,0:55:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,our status wins,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.37,0:55:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the alliance wins,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.37,0:55:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,if I set it up so that everybody wins
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.37,0:55:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,then I have no enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.37,0:55:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I have no enemies,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.37,0:55:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,you see, there is no negative energy
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.37,0:55:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,opposing the direction of the positive support of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.37,0:55:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that flourishes,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.37,0:55:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that flows forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.37,0:55:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So all of life then is experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.37,0:55:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,as an enhancement of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.43,0:55:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,To hold life then from a win-win position.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.43,0:55:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So one of the things,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.43,0:55:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the good implications
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.43,0:55:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,for a well- escuelaed brand
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.43,0:55:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is that there's a lot of
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.59,0:56:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,win-win situation all around and one of acknowledged great success way to become
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.77,0:56:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,a success is to make your boss a success instead of going into competition with
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.67,0:56:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,them you see in which somebody is bound to lose making your boss a success moves
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.09,0:56:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,him up the ladder and creates a space for you to move up to come from a
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.09,0:56:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,competitive position would mean to defeat the boss that would bring up the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.01,0:56:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,unconscious anxiety distress of the fear of retaliation in a war as you
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.13,0:56:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,picture it a war then you've defeated the opponent and of course now his
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.67,0:56:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,friends are going to come and get you and so you would have to live ever after
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.27,0:56:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,in a position of danger and defensiveness so there's willingness
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.41,0:56:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,then to give up the adversary position to become more easygoing you can see the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.97,0:56:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,amount of stress experienced by the easygoing person does easygoing mean
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.83,0:56:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,vulnerable
